response.overview: Quincy Carr is the 'Quality Comedy King' for his style of clean adult humor called Quality Comedy. Although, he thinks he looks way too young to be 40; his body says otherwise! Enjoy this laugh out loud stand up performance as Quincy shares some of his most outrageous experiences he recently encountered from scary visits to his primary care doctor, an encounter with his abusive biological father, his eye opening revelation on racism, and his spot on observation(s) of over confident people!
response.title: Quincy Carr: Too Young for 40
